Nollywood actress, Uche Okoye has threatened to kill herself after she was snubbed on social media by Nigerian singer Wizkid. Okoye
who took to her Instagram page to express her love for the singer,
however, gave him one week ultimatum to follow her back on social media
and recognise her love or be ready to receive the news of her death. In a video posted on Instagram, she warned Wizkid to stop playing with her heart. “Am
back again, am back again. It’s me and Wizkid today, you can’t be
messing with my heart and expect me to lay back. I have had it up to
here. Today I have come for you and I to settle it. “Wizkid!
You can’t be messing with my heart like that na, check it. Is it
proper?, is it right? No!. I have being a fan since way back. I like
this dude. I have being tagging this dude. he won’t say he does not know
me.” (NAN)